# Exception: vendored TRT-export shims must stay tracked (Slice 2 of trt-migration).
# These two files replace torch.rand/randn_like with ONNX-compatible equivalents
# and guard int-vs-tensor length checks; removing them breaks TRT ONNX export.
!RVC/infer/lib/infer_pack/models_onnx.py
!RVC/infer/lib/infer_pack/attentions_onnx.py
